{"title":"谚语","authors":[],"dates":[{"year":1957,"month":3,"day":9}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"谚语"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"酒量小的人喝两杯就会天旋地转；骄傲的人稍受表扬就不知天高地厚。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"＊"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"虚心的人总是学十算一，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"自满的人总是学一当十。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"＊"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"上阵的骏马勒紧缰绳还想奔，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"睡觉的懒猪驱它去吃食也不想动。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"＊"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有理走遍天下，无理寸步难行。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"＊"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不实心不成事，不虚心不知事。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不是靠天吃饭，全靠双手动弹。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"＊"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三天不念口生，三天不做手生。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"＊"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一人不如二人计，三人打个大主意。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"＊"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千斤绳从细处烂起。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}